  <diagram name="L1 — System Context">&lt;mxGraphModel dx=&quot;1422&quot; dy=&quot;762&quot; grid=&quot;1&quot; gridSize=&quot;10&quot; guides=&quot;1&quot; tooltips=&quot;1&quot; connect=&quot;1&quot; arrows=&quot;1&quot; fold=&quot;1&quot; page=&quot;1&quot; pageScale=&quot;1&quot; pageWidth=&quot;1654&quot; pageHeight=&quot;1169&quot; math=&quot;0&quot; shadow=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;root&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;tb&quot; value=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;fillColor=#003087;strokeColor=none;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;0&quot; y=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;1654&quot; height=&quot;78&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;tt&quot; value=&quot;C4 System Context — Agent JWT Role Claimant Enhancement&quot; style=&quot;text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=20;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#ffffff;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;0&quot; y=&quot;8&quot; width=&quot;1654&quot; height=&quot;36&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;ts&quot; value=&quot;DECISION-4860  |  Level 1: System Context  |  Who interacts with the ICB Authentication Platform and how?&quot; style=&quot;text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=11;fontColor=#b0c4de;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;0&quot; y=&quot;46&quot; width=&quot;1654&quot; height=&quot;26&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;agent&quot; value=&quot;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;Salesforce Agent&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#1a3a6e&amp;quot;&amp;gt;[Person]&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#333&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Banking operations agent. Logs into Salesforce to manage cases and approvals. Actions may or may not involve a customer (party key).&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&quot; style=&quot;shape=mxgraph.basic.person2;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#003087;fontColor=#003087;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=4;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;100&quot; y=&quot;115&quot; width=&quot;160&quot; height=&quot;180&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;sf&quot; value=&quot;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;Salesforce CRM&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#555&amp;quot;&amp;gt;[External System]&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#444&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Agent UI. Authenticates via SAML. Sends internal JWT with agent role to ICB Platform. Passes access token on API calls.&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&quot; style=&quot;rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999999;fontColor=#333333;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=top;arcSize=4;spacingTop=5;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;70&quot; y=&quot;390&quot; width=&quot;210&quot; height=&quot;160&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;ida&quot; value=&quot;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;IDAnywhere SAML IdP&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#555&amp;quot;&amp;gt;[External System]&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#444&amp;quot;&amp;gt;SAML Identity Provider for agent SSO. ⚠ Roles tied to Salesforce SEAL ID — cannot be used directly in ForgeRock context.&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&quot; style=&quot;rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999999;fontColor=#333333;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=top;arcSize=4;spacingTop=5;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;380&quot; y=&quot;115&quot; width=&quot;220&quot; height=&quot;160&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;icb&quot; value=&quot;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;ICB Authentication Platform&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:10px;color:#e0e8ff&amp;quot;&amp;gt;[Software System]&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:10px;color:#c7d8f5&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Issues colleague access tokens with CRM role embedded.&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;Validates tokens on inbound API calls.&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;Extracts CRM_ROLE and forwards to Florence for RBAC enforcement.&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&quot; style=&quot;rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#1e40af;strokeColor=#003087;fontColor=#ffffff;fontSize=13;verticalAlign=top;arcSize=4;spacingTop=8;fontStyle=1;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;700&quot; y=&quot;350&quot; width=&quot;380&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;florence&quot; value=&quot;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;Florence Case Manager&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#555&amp;quot;&amp;gt;[External System]&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#444&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Enforces RBAC on case and approval operations. Reads CRM_ROLE from Jpmorgan-Authorization-Attribute header. No changes needed.&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&quot; style=&quot;rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999999;fontColor=#333333;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=top;arcSize=4;spacingTop=5;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;1300&quot; y=&quot;350&quot; width=&quot;210&quot; height=&quot;180&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;e1&quot; value=&quot;Login &amp;amp; perform actions&quot; style=&quot;edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;strokeColor=#003087;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=#003087;fontSize=9;&quot; edge=&quot;1&quot; source=&quot;agent&quot; target=&quot;sf&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry relative=&quot;1&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;e2&quot; value=&quot;SAMLRequest&quot; style=&quot;edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;strokeColor=#888;strokeWidth=1.5;fontColor=#555;fontSize=9;dashed=1;dashPattern=6 3;exitX=1;exitY=0.25;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;&quot; edge=&quot;1&quot; source=&quot;sf&quot; target=&quot;ida&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry relative=&quot;1&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot;&gt;&lt;Array as=&quot;points&quot;&gt;&lt;mxPoint x=&quot;320&quot; y=&quot;430&quot; /&gt;&lt;mxPoint x=&quot;320&quot; y=&quot;195&quot; /&gt;&lt;/Array&gt;&lt;/mxGeometry&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;e3&quot; value=&quot;SAMLResponse + SAML Token&quot; style=&quot;edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;strokeColor=#888;strokeWidth=1.5;fontColor=#555;fontSize=9;dashed=1;dashPattern=6 3;exitX=0;exitY=0.7;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=1;entryY=0.2;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;&quot; edge=&quot;1&quot; source=&quot;ida&quot; target=&quot;sf&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry relative=&quot;1&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot;&gt;&lt;Array as=&quot;points&quot;&gt;&lt;mxPoint x=&quot;350&quot; y=&quot;330&quot; /&gt;&lt;mxPoint x=&quot;350&quot; y=&quot;445&quot; /&gt;&lt;/Array&gt;&lt;/mxGeometry&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;e4&quot; value=&quot;Token exchange + internal JWT (chase.role)  🆕 NEW&quot; style=&quot;edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;strokeColor=#d97706;strokeWidth=2.5;fontColor=#92400e;fontSize=9;fontStyle=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.4;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.35;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;&quot; edge=&quot;1&quot; source=&quot;sf&quot; target=&quot;icb&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry relative=&quot;1&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;e5&quot; value=&quot;Colleague token with CRM_ROLE embedded  🆕 NEW&quot; style=&quot;edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;strokeColor=#d97706;strokeWidth=2.5;fontColor=#92400e;fontSize=9;fontStyle=1;exitX=0;exitY=0.65;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=1;entryY=0.55;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;&quot; edge=&quot;1&quot; source=&quot;icb&quot; target=&quot;sf&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry relative=&quot;1&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;e6&quot; value=&quot;API call — OBO token (customer, partyKey)  ✅ existing&quot; style=&quot;edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;strokeColor=#059669;strokeWidth=2.5;fontColor=#065f46;fontSize=9;exitX=1;exitY=0.6;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.6;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;&quot; edge=&quot;1&quot; source=&quot;sf&quot; target=&quot;icb&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry relative=&quot;1&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;e7&quot; value=&quot;API call — Colleague token (non-customer)  🆕 NEW&quot; style=&quot;edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;strokeColor=#d97706;strokeWidth=2.5;fontColor=#92400e;fontSize=9;fontStyle=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.75;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.75;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;&quot; edge=&quot;1&quot; source=&quot;sf&quot; target=&quot;icb&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry relative=&quot;1&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;e8&quot; value=&quot;Jpmorgan-Authorization-Attribute: jpmc.crm.role=CRM_ROLE&quot; style=&quot;edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;strokeColor=#1d4ed8;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=#1e3a8a;fontSize=9;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;&quot; edge=&quot;1&quot; source=&quot;icb&quot; target=&quot;florence&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry relative=&quot;1&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;n1&quot; value=&quot;💡 Key Insight: When agent acts on a customer (party key exists) → OBO token used (role already present ✅). When no customer / no party key → Colleague token used. Role was missing ❌ → this change adds it 🆕&quot; style=&quot;rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#eff6ff;strokeColor=#1d4ed8;fontColor=#1e3a8a;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;380&quot; y=&quot;640&quot; width=&quot;940&quot; height=&quot;60&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;lb&quot; value=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#cccccc;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;30&quot; y=&quot;760&quot; width=&quot;280&quot; height=&quot;165&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;lh&quot; value=&quot;Legend&quot; style=&quot;text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#333;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;45&quot; y=&quot;766&quot; width=&quot;150&quot; height=&quot;22&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;le1&quot; value=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#d97706;strokeWidth=2.5;&quot; edge=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry relative=&quot;1&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot;&gt;&lt;mxPoint x=&quot;50&quot; y=&quot;796&quot; as=&quot;sourcePoint&quot; /&gt;&lt;mxPoint x=&quot;100&quot; y=&quot;796&quot; as=&quot;targetPoint&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxGeometry&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;ll1&quot; value=&quot;New / Modified (this change)&quot; style=&quot;text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;fontSize=10;fontColor=#555;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;108&quot; y=&quot;789&quot; width=&quot;190&quot; height=&quot;20&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;le2&quot; value=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#059669;strokeWidth=2.5;&quot; edge=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry relative=&quot;1&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot;&gt;&lt;mxPoint x=&quot;50&quot; y=&quot;826&quot; as=&quot;sourcePoint&quot; /&gt;&lt;mxPoint x=&quot;100&quot; y=&quot;826&quot; as=&quot;targetPoint&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxGeometry&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;ll2&quot; value=&quot;Existing flow (working)&quot; style=&quot;text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;fontSize=10;fontColor=#555;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;108&quot; y=&quot;819&quot; width=&quot;190&quot; height=&quot;20&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;le3&quot; value=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#1d4ed8;strokeWidth=2;&quot; edge=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry relative=&quot;1&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot;&gt;&lt;mxPoint x=&quot;50&quot; y=&quot;856&quot; as=&quot;sourcePoint&quot; /&gt;&lt;mxPoint x=&quot;100&quot; y=&quot;856&quot; as=&quot;targetPoint&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxGeometry&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;ll3&quot; value=&quot;Role forwarded to Florence&quot; style=&quot;text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;fontSize=10;fontColor=#555;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;108&quot; y=&quot;849&quot; width=&quot;190&quot; height=&quot;20&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;le4&quot; value=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#888;strokeWidth=1.5;dashed=1;dashPattern=6 3;&quot; edge=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry relative=&quot;1&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot;&gt;&lt;mxPoint x=&quot;50&quot; y=&quot;886&quot; as=&quot;sourcePoint&quot; /&gt;&lt;mxPoint x=&quot;100&quot; y=&quot;886&quot; as=&quot;targetPoint&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxGeometry&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;ll4&quot; value=&quot;SAML authentication&quot; style=&quot;text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;fontSize=10;fontColor=#555;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;108&quot; y=&quot;879&quot; width=&quot;190&quot; height=&quot;20&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;/root&gt;&lt;/mxGraphModel&gt;</diagram>
  <diagram name="L2 — Container">&lt;mxGraphModel dx=&quot;1422&quot; dy=&quot;762&quot; grid=&quot;1&quot; gridSize=&quot;10&quot; guides=&quot;1&quot; tooltips=&quot;1&quot; connect=&quot;1&quot; arrows=&quot;1&quot; fold=&quot;1&quot; page=&quot;1&quot; pageScale=&quot;1&quot; pageWidth=&quot;1654&quot; pageHeight=&quot;1100&quot; math=&quot;0&quot; shadow=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;root&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;tb&quot; value=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;fillColor=#003087;strokeColor=none;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;0&quot; y=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;1654&quot; height=&quot;78&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;tt&quot; value=&quot;C4 Container Diagram — Agent JWT Role Claimant Enhancement&quot; style=&quot;text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=20;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#ffffff;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;0&quot; y=&quot;8&quot; width=&quot;1654&quot; height=&quot;36&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;ts&quot; value=&quot;DECISION-4860  |  Level 2: Container  |  ICB Authentication Platform&quot; style=&quot;text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=11;fontColor=#b0c4de;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;0&quot; y=&quot;47&quot; width=&quot;1654&quot; height=&quot;26&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;agent&quot; value=&quot;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;Salesforce Agent&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#1e3a8a&amp;quot;&amp;gt;[Person]&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#333&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Banking ops agent. Performs case &amp;amp;amp; approval actions in Salesforce.&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&quot; style=&quot;shape=mxgraph.basic.person2;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#003087;fontColor=#003087;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=4;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;55&quot; y=&quot;95&quot; width=&quot;150&quot; height=&quot;165&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;ida&quot; value=&quot;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;IDAnywhere SAML IdP&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#555&amp;quot;&amp;gt;[External System | SAML 2.0]&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#444&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Provides SAML assertion for agent SSO.&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;⚠ Roles tied to Salesforce SEAL ID&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;— cannot be used in ForgeRock context.&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&quot; style=&quot;rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0f0f0;strokeColor=#888888;fontColor=#333333;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=top;arcSize=4;spacingTop=5;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;310&quot; y=&quot;95&quot; width=&quot;215&quot; height=&quot;165&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;sf&quot; value=&quot;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;Salesforce CRM&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#555&amp;quot;&amp;gt;[External System | Salesforce Lightning]&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#444&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Agent UI. Authenticates via SAML.&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;Sends internal JWT with &amp;lt;b&amp;gt;chase.role&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;to ForgeRock on token exchange.&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;Calls Case Manager with:&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;• OBO token (customer / partyKey)&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;• Colleague token (non-customer)&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&quot; style=&quot;rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0f0f0;strokeColor=#888888;fontColor=#333333;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=top;arcSize=4;spacingTop=5;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;40&quot; y=&quot;330&quot; width=&quot;195&quot; height=&quot;230&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;bnd&quot; value=&quot;ICB Authentication Platform&quot; style=&quot;rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0f4ff;strokeColor=#1d4ed8;strokeDasharray=10 5;fontColor=#1d4ed8;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;arcSize=2;spacingTop=8;spacingLeft=12;align=left;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;320&quot; y=&quot;270&quot; width=&quot;980&quot; height=&quot;700&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;fr&quot; value=&quot;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;ICB TMS ForgeRock&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#1e3a8a&amp;quot;&amp;gt;[Container | ForgeRock AM 7.x]&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#1e3a8a&amp;quot;&amp;gt;① Receives token exchange + internal JWT from Salesforce.&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;② Validates Salesforce JWT signature.&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;③ Extracts &amp;lt;b&amp;gt;chase.role&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt; claim.&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;④ Issues colleague token with &amp;lt;b&amp;gt;CRM_ROLE&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt; embedded.&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&quot; style=&quot;rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dbeafe;strokeColor=#1d4ed8;fontColor=#1e3a8a;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=top;arcSize=4;spacingTop=5;&quot; vertex=&quot;1&quot; parent=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;mxGeometry x=&quot;360&quot; y=&quot;310&quot; width=&quot;285&quot; height=&quot;195&quot; as=&quot;geometry&quot; /&gt;&lt;/mxCell&gt;&lt;mxCell id=&quot;cm&quot; value=&quot;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;ICB Case Manager&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font style=&amp;quot;font-size:9px;color:#1e3a8a&amp;quot;&amp;gt;[Container | Sprin